title: Corumbaense Futebol Clube
text: The Corumbaense Futebol Clube, usually known simply as Corumbaense, is a Brazilian <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Corumb%C3%A1">Corumbá</a> in the state of <a href="Mato%20Grosso%20do%20Sul">Mato Grosso do Sul</a>. Established in 1914. The club competed in the <a href="Campeonato%20Brasileiro%20S%C3%A9rie%20A">Campeonato Brasileiro Série A</a> in 1985.
